<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
    *{
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }
    p{
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 12px;
        
    }
    h6{
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 12px;
        
    }
    .details{
        background-color:#e4e4e4;
        display: inline-flex;
        width: 570px;
        height: 20px;
        padding: 5px;
    }
    .container {
    max-width: 600px;
    height: 45px;
    background: url('https://storage.googleapis.com/diahome-com-bucket-1/Image/Rectangle.png');
    }
    .container__image {
    width: 150px;
    float: left;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    margin-left: 15px;
    margin-top: 5px; 
  }
  .container__text {
    text-align: right;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    margin-right: 20px;
    margin-top: 30px;
    padding: 2px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img class="container__image" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/diahome-com-bucket-1/Image/logo_name.png"/>
        <div class="container__text">
          <p style="font-size: 8px;margin-top: 11px">Call us at<span>:</span>7540001234</p>
          <p style="font-size: 8px;">Download the Diahome App</p>
       </div>
    </div>
        <br>
    <div style="padding-left: 20px;">
        <p style="font-weight: bold;">Dear {{doctorName}},</p>
        <br>
        <p>This is a reminder for your appointment. Here are the details of your appointment.</p>
        <br>
    </div>
    <div style="padding-left: 20px;">
        <h6 class="details"><span style="width: 150px; height: 20px;"> Patient Name - </span><span style="font-weight: bold;">{{patientFirstName}} {{patientLastName}}</span></h6> 
    </div>
    <div style="padding-left: 20px;">
        <h6 class="details"><span style="width: 150px;height: 20px;"> Date & Time - </span><span style="font-weight: bold;">{{date}} at {{time}}</span></h6>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div style="font-weight: bold;padding-left: 20px;">
                      
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
        <td>
        <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
            <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#152A75" style="padding: 12px 18px 12px 18px; border-radius:3px" align="center"><a href="https://doctor.diahome.com" target="_blank" style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;">Visit Doctor's Portal &rarr;</a></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div style="font-weight: bold;padding-left: 20px;">
        <p>Regards,</p>
        <p>Team Diahome</p>
        <br>
    </div>
    <div style="font-weight: lighter;color: gray;font-size: 8px;padding-left: 20px;">
        <p>You are receiving this email because you are registered on the Diahome app.This email is meant to</p>
        <p>communicate about your appointment/care and is not meant for promotional purposes.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>